# Gherkin Specs First

Before fixing a bug or implementing a feature, write Gherkin scenarios in `specs/` that describe the expected behavior.

## Format

```gherkin
Feature: <feature name>

  Scenario: <scenario name>
    Given <precondition>
    When <action>
    Then <expected outcome>
```

## Rules

- Place specs in `specs/<feature-name>.feature`
- Cover the happy path and key edge cases
- Scenarios must reflect actual user-observable behavior, not implementation details
- Commit the spec file before writing any code
